The graphics are the best I've seen on ps2 yet, I spent about 2 hours just running around Guadosalam taking it all in <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   The FF movie definetly had some influence on this game, since the cinematics are the best in any FF yet.<br>
Music is as good as any FF game out there, but Uematsu isn't one of my favorite composers (Mitsuda or maybe the people behind the Suikoden soundtracks are my faves).  I do like the fact that X has a wide variety of musical styles in it though, all 3 of the playstation FF's had good soundtracks but suffered from lack of variety.<br>
The levelling system is amazing, the sphere grid is very hard to explain but simple to understand, and random battles (as well as boss battles) are actually fun again!  The summoning system has also been refined yet again, in one of it's best incarnations yet.<br>
Overall, the game is a masterpiece.  An absolute must have for any rpg fans... I know I won't be interested to play any other games at all until I've beaten it.  After I finished FFIX I didn't feel like the series had been furthered at all (as much as everyone hated VIII, I do give it props for taking some bold steps away from the FF tradition, with the junction system, level system and theme) but Square regained the ground they lost and made up for it with FFX.  Without a doubt the RPG of the year, if not game of the year. (haven't played GTA3 yet <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=19794">Miery Van Houten</a><br><a href="http://www.triadcontinuum.com">Triad Continuum</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulargebarukungukbarsh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Large Barukungukbarsh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>THE Oracle</span><br>  Posts: 1300<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/28/01 9:17:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5764.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: owns</span><hr size=1> FF10 is amazing. Buy it.<br>
